room_title: Escape room "Buried Alive by a Creepy Dude" by Gnarly Escapes in Idaho Falls
room_description: You’re walking down the sidewalk with your companions minding your own business when you feel a sharp twinge in your neck.  Everything goes black. The next thing you know you wake up in a wooden box. You’re trapped, but your companions are next to you in a boxes of their own. Now you must work together to get out before your kidnapper returns. A game for up to 8 people. Choose your partners wisely…
